videos.description: Oregon's Tony Brooks-James takes the handoff and rushes 7 yards into the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Oregon strikes first on Brooks-James' TD

videos.description: Oregon QB Justin Herbert tosses a 7-yard pass into the end zone to TE Jacob Breeland, who makes the catch to extend the Ducks' lead.
videos.headline: Herbert connects with Breeland on short TD pass

videos.description: Stanford QB K.J. Costello tosses a pass into the end zone to WR JJ Arcega-Whiteside, who leaps high to make the catch for the score.
videos.headline: Arcega-Whiteside jumps to secure TD

videos.description: Oregon RB CJ Verdell finds the hole and speeds 48 yards into the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Verdell breaks free for 48-yard TD run

videos.description: The Oregon Ducks hold a 24-7 lead over Stanford at halftime after a strong offensive play from both Justin Herbert and CJ Verdell.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Oregon takes control in the first half) 2018/09/22 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Oregon takes control in the first half

videos.description: A high snap goes over the head of Justin Herbert, allowing Stanford's Joey Alfieri to scoop up the ball and return it 80 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Alfieri gives Stanford life with scoop-and-score

videos.description: Bryce Love rushes 22 yards and just gets inside the pylon for a Stanford TD and officials say play stands after review.
videos.headline: Love just sneaks inside pylon for TD

videos.description: Stanford attempts to convert on fourth down, but RB Cameron Scarlett gets stuffed by Oregon's defense as the Cardinal turn it over on downs.
videos.headline: Ducks' defense comes up big on fourth down

videos.description: Oregon RB Cyrus Habibi-Likio takes the handoff, dives past a tackle and into the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Habibi-Likio dives through tackle for TD

videos.description: Stanford QB K.J. Costello connects with JJ Arcega-Whiteside on a 15-yard touchdown pass to bring the Cardinal's deficit to 31-28 late in the fourth.
videos.headline: Arcega-Whiteside's TD catch inches Stanford closer

videos.description: Oregon RB CJ Verdell rushes forward and has the ball pop loose. Stanford's Sean Barton recovers it with less than a minute left.
videos.headline: Barton comes up with crucial fumble recovery for Stanford

videos.description: Stanford kicker Jet Toner connects on a game-tying, 32-yard field goal as time expires to force overtime.
videos.headline: Toner sends game to OT with 32-yard FG

videos.description: Stanford QB K.J. Costello tosses a pass towards the end zone to Colby Parkinson, who tips the ball over a defender to secure the touchdown.
videos.headline: Parkinson tips ball to himself for TD

videos.description: Justin Herbert's pass gets deflected in the end zone and Stanford's Alameen Murphy picks it off to give the Cardinal a 38-31 win in overtime.
videos.headline: Murphy seals Stanford's comeback win with INT

videos.description: Stanford head coach David Shaw explains how special Bryce Love and K.J. Costello are after their comeback win over Oregon.
videos.headline: Shaw praises the performances of Love's and Costello's

videos.description: K.J. Costello and Bryce Love break down how Stanford was able to regroup at halftime and lead the Cardinal to a 38-31 comeback win against Oregon.
videos.headline: Costello says Stanford's focus led to comeback win

videos.description: After facing a 17-point deficit at halftime, the Stanford Cardinal storm back to tie the game as time expires and seal the win in overtime.
